{"_id":"post-8c7342e4-ffc8-4df5-9bbe-3e31944aba9c","_type":"post","title":"Multitabs","slug":{"_type":"slug","current":"multitabs"},"body":[{"_key":"bbad4ff6fd21","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Repl.it is a great place for prototyping ideas and starting new projects. However as your projects get bigger, the editing experience starts feeling a little limited. That's why we're exciting to announce that we're adding support for tabs!","_key":"bbad4ff6fd210"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"4b6fd0976999","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"With the new multitab layout, you can open files in new tabs so that you can quickly switch back to them later.","_key":"4b6fd09769990"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"679cee96c8c6","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"There are a few ways of opening a file in a new tab:","_key":"679cee96c8c60"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"cd7668c4c028","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":["code"],"text":"Ctrl + Click","_key":"cd7668c4c0280"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" (or ","_key":"cd7668c4c0281"},{"_type":"span","marks":["code"],"text":"Cmd + Click","_key":"cd7668c4c0282"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" on MacOS) the file in the filetree","_key":"cd7668c4c0283"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":1,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"5939ac3715df","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Drag the file from the filetree directly onto the header or onto an open tab in the header","_key":"5939ac3715df0"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":1,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"98884441d92e","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Right click on the file and hit \"Open tab\" in the menu","_key":"98884441d92e0"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":1,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"ac63db62cd55","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"From there, you can hit the \"X\" to the right of the file name to close the tab.","_key":"ac63db62cd550"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"d01a5bf66bc4","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Here's a demo of what that looks like:","_key":"d01a5bf66bc40"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"6acd064a018b","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"6acd064a018b0","text":"","marks":[]}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"c749230bc2ed","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"You can also drag tabs around to reorder them like so:","_key":"c749230bc2ed0"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"16742395546a","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"16742395546a0","text":"","marks":[]}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"0675654cb613","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"We hope this makes it easier to build larger projects on Repl.it. Happy hacking!","_key":"0675654cb6130"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal"}],"publishedAt":"2020-07-02T00:00:00.000Z"}